            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Chronicles%2015%3A1-16%3A36%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_1%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Chronicles%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EPreparing%20to%20Move%20the%20Ark%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20now%20built%20several%20buildings%20for%20himself%20in%20the%20City%20of%20David.%20He%20also%20prepared%20a%20place%20for%20the%20Ark%20of%20God%20and%20set%20up%20a%20special%20tent%20for%20it.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_2%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20commanded%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BNo%20one%20except%20the%20Levites%20may%20carry%20the%20Ark%20of%20God.%20The%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20chosen%20them%20to%20carry%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20to%20serve%20him%20forever.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_3%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20summoned%20all%20Israel%20to%20Jerusalem%20to%20bring%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20to%20the%20place%20he%20had%20prepared%20for%20it.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_4%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20number%20of%20the%20descendants%20of%20Aaron%20(the%20priests)%20and%20the%20Levites%20who%20were%20called%20together%3A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_5%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20clan%20of%20Kohath%2C%20120%2C%20with%20Uriel%20as%20their%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_6%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20clan%20of%20Merari%2C%20220%2C%20with%20Asaiah%20as%20their%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_7%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20clan%20of%20Gershon%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E15%3A7%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3EGershom%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20variant%20spelling%20of%20Gershon.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20130%2C%20with%20Joel%20as%20their%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_8%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20descendants%20of%20Elizaphan%2C%20200%2C%20with%20Shemaiah%20as%20their%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_9%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20descendants%20of%20Hebron%2C%2080%2C%20with%20Eliel%20as%20their%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_10%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-hanging%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EFrom%20the%20descendants%20of%20Uzziel%2C%20112%2C%20with%20Amminadab%20as%20their%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_11%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20David%20summoned%20the%20priests%2C%20Zadok%20and%20Abiathar%2C%20and%20these%20Levite%20leaders%3A%20Uriel%2C%20Asaiah%2C%20Joel%2C%20Shemaiah%2C%20Eliel%2C%20and%20Amminadab.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_12%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20said%20to%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYou%20are%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Levite%20families.%20You%20must%20purify%20yourselves%20and%20all%20your%20fellow%20Levites%2C%20so%20you%20can%20bring%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20to%20the%20place%20I%20have%20prepared%20for%20it.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_13%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EBecause%20you%20Levites%20did%20not%20carry%20the%20Ark%20the%20first%20time%2C%20the%20anger%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20our%20God%20burst%20out%20against%20us.%20We%20failed%20to%20ask%20God%20how%20to%20move%20it%20properly.%26%23x201D%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_14%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20priests%20and%20the%20Levites%20purified%20themselves%20in%20order%20to%20bring%20the%20Ark%20of%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20the%20God%20of%20Israel%2C%20to%20Jerusalem.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_15%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20Levites%20carried%20the%20Ark%20of%20God%20on%20their%20shoulders%20with%20its%20carrying%20poles%2C%20just%20as%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20instructed%20Moses.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_16%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EDavid%20also%20ordered%20the%20Levite%20leaders%20to%20appoint%20a%20choir%20of%20Levites%20who%20were%20singers%20and%20musicians%20to%20sing%20joyful%20songs%20to%20the%20accompaniment%20of%20harps%2C%20lyres%2C%20and%20cymbals.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_17%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20the%20Levites%20appointed%20Heman%20son%20of%20Joel%20along%20with%20his%20fellow%20Levites%3A%20Asaph%20son%20of%20Berekiah%2C%20and%20Ethan%20son%20of%20Kushaiah%20from%20the%20clan%20of%20Merari.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_18%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20following%20men%20were%20chosen%20as%20their%20assistants%3A%20Zechariah%2C%20Jaaziel%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E15%3A18%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20several%20Hebrew%20manuscripts%20and%20Greek%20version%20(see%20also%20parallel%20lists%20in%2015%3A20%3B%2016%3A5)%3B%20Masoretic%20Text%20reads%20%3Cem%3EZechariah%20ben%20Jaaziel.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Shemiramoth%2C%20Jehiel%2C%20Unni%2C%20Eliab%2C%20Benaiah%2C%20Maaseiah%2C%20Mattithiah%2C%20Eliphelehu%2C%20Mikneiah%2C%20and%20the%20gatekeepers%26%23x2014%3BObed-edom%20and%20Jeiel.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22chr1_15_19%22%20bk%3D%22chr1%22%20ch%3D%2215%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20musicians%20Heman%2C%20Asaph%2C%20and%20Ethan%20were%20chosen%20to%20sound%20the%20bronze%20cymba